---
---

<section class="relative">
  <div class="section-divider"></div>
  <div class="py-[var(--section-py)] px-6 sm:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 md:gap-16">
        <!-- Left column: label + photo -->
        <div class="md:col-span-4">
          <p class="text-[var(--text-label)] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-[var(--color-text-subtle)] mb-8" data-animate>Sobre mim</p>

          <!-- Photo with rotating gradient ring -->
          <div class="relative w-48 h-48 sm:w-56 sm:h-56" data-animate>
            <!-- Rotating gradient ring -->
            <div class="about-photo-ring absolute inset-[-4px] rounded-full" style="background: conic-gradient(#FA5D29, #f97316, #fbbf24, #FA5D29);"></div>
            <div class="w-full h-full rounded-full bg-[var(--color-bg)] relative overflow-hidden" style="padding: 3px;">
              <div class="w-full h-full rounded-full bg-[var(--color-text)] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
                <!-- Replace with: <img src="/francisco.png" alt="Francisco Sousa" class="w-full h-full object-cover" /> when photo is available -->
                <span class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-light text-[var(--color-bg)] tracking-tight">FS</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Floating badge: top-right -->
            <div class="about-badge absolute -top-2 -right-4 bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white text-[var(--text-xs)] font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-lg">
              Full-Stack Dev
            </div>

            <!-- Floating badge: bottom-left -->
            <div class="about-badge about-badge-alt absolute -bottom-2 -left-4 bg-[var(--color-text)] text-[var(--color-bg)] text-[var(--text-xs)] font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-lg" style="animation-delay: 1.5s;">
              Flutter &middot; Astro
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Availability -->
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-2" data-animate>
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-[var(--color-whatsapp)] rounded-full"></span>
            <span class="text-[var(--text-xs)] text-[var(--color-text-subtle)]">Dispon&iacute;vel para novos projetos</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right column: bio -->
        <div class="md:col-span-8 md:pt-12">
          <h2 class="font-light tracking-tight leading-[0.95] mb-10" style="font-size: var(--text-h1);" data-animate>
            Ol&aacute;, eu sou o Francisco.
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-lg font-light leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            <p data-animate>
              Cresci em Cascais, entre o mar e o skatepark. Antes de escrever c&oacute;digo, dava aulas de skate &mdash; e foi a&iacute; que aprendi que ensinar &eacute; a melhor forma de comunicar. Hoje aplico a mesma clareza a cada projeto que construo.
            </p>
            <p data-animate>
              Sou developer full-stack e crio websites, aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es m&oacute;veis e plataformas digitais para neg&oacute;cios que querem crescer online. Trabalho diretamente consigo &mdash; sem ag&ecirc;ncia, sem intermedi&aacute;rios, sem burocracia.
            </p>
            <p data-animate>
              Quando fala comigo, fala com quem vai desenhar, construir e entregar o seu projeto do in&iacute;cio ao fim. &Eacute; assim que garanto que tudo fica exatamente como precisa.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Value props — clean, minimal -->
          <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8" data-animate>
            <div>
              <p class="text-[var(--color-text)] font-light text-2xl tracking-tight mb-2">50/50</p>
              <p class="text-[var(--text-small)] text-[var(--color-text-subtle)]">S&oacute; paga quando estiver satisfeito</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-[var(--color-text)] font-light text-2xl tracking-tight mb-2">WhatsApp</p>
              <p class="text-[var(--text-small)] text-[var(--color-text-subtle)]">Contacto direto, sem intermedi&aacute;rios</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-[var(--color-text)] font-light text-2xl tracking-tight mb-2">30 dias</p>
              <p class="text-[var(--text-small)] text-[var(--color-text-subtle)]">Suporte gr&aacute;tis ap&oacute;s entrega</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes spin-ring {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }

  .about-photo-ring {
    animation: spin-ring 4s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes float-badge {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-6px); }
  }

  .about-badge {
    animation: float-badge 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .about-badge-alt {
    animation: float-badge 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    animation-delay: 1.5s;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .about-photo-ring {
      animation: none;
    }
    .about-badge,
    .about-badge-alt {
      animation: none;
    }
  }
</style>
